      "content": "It's easy to get caught up in the accumulation of experiences and forget about the desire for stability and permanence. Your body and mind may be craving a sense of rest and routine, a chance to settle into a single location and let the familiarity of home and tradition sink back in. Sometimes, the endpoint of a journey can feel more like a return to normalcy than a completion. Is there a particular place or style of life that you're craving to find in this next phase of your life?",
      "source": "target",
