    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not about finding a new home or a routine. i mean... when i say \"stop for good,\" i don't mean finding a house. i mean the actual end of the trip. the part where you don't have to pack a bag or worry about the next destination ever again. just total stillness. everything just... fading out. does that make sense?",
